---
title: Mustard and Herb-Crusted Pork with Roasted Potatoes and Broccoli
description: Super simple to throw together and packed with flavour, this crusted pork loin is a star. The crisp broccoli and tender, golden potatoes are complemented perfectly with a tasty pan sauce. Best part? It will all be on your plate in no time!
